.Dd October 18, 2021
.Dt PTEE 1
.Os
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm ptee
.Nd tee for PTYs
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl t Ar ms
.Ar command ...
.Cm >
.Ar file
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
runs
.Ar command
in a new PTY
which is mirrored to
the current PTY
and standard output.
Standard output must be redirected
to a file or pipe.
.
.Pp
Type
.Ic ^S
to write a media copy sequence
to standard output.
Type
.Ic ^Q
to toggle writing to standard output.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl t Ar ms
Write a media copy sequence
to standard output every
.Ar ms
milliseconds.
.El
.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr script 1
.
.Sh BUGS
Window size changes are not propagated
to the child PTY.
